          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "stack of high purity 23 microns of Fe foils. Several",
                "Cu foils were placed into the stack for monitoring of",
                "the beam intensity and the energy distribution along",
                "the stack"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".18 MeV and 14.5 MeV primary proton",
                "energy. Beam current measurement by Faraday cup and",
                "via monnitor reaction on Cu. The energy dagradation",
                "was calculated according to J.F.Ziegler, The stopping",
                "and ranges of ions in matter, vol 3, (Pergamon, New",
                "York, 1977) and was controlled by monitor reactions",
                "on Cu. The decay data were taken from E. Browne and",
                "R.B.Fierstone, Table of radioisotopes, (ed. Shirley)",
                "Wiley, New York, 1986."
              ]
            }
          ],
